  <h1>This is some funny HTML code!</h1>
  <p>Here is a list of some funny HTML tags:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><b>blink</b> - This tag makes the text blink.</li>
    <li><marquee>This text will scroll across the screen.</marquee></li>
    <li><font color="hotpink">This text will be pink.</font></li>
    <li><strike>This text will be crossed out.</strike></li>
    <li><big>This text will be big.</big></li>
    <li><small>This text will be small.</small></li>
  </ul>
